{"tid":1382882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我同樣作為一住咗係元朗26年嘅人見到佢咁打真係好撚嬲 ！！！","createTime":"2019-07-29T14:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T15:20:25.000Z","uid":22819,"like":105,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"93a2786723bd6b17929680df08611be7c3300a61","tid":1382882,"uid":22819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:44:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">代朋友Post</span></span><br />\n我同樣作為一住咗係元朗26年嘅人見到佢咁打真係好撚嬲 ！！！<br />\n杜夏嬋<br />\nTel 93390693<br />\n嗇色園可道中學<br />\nIg傳送門:<br />\n杜小姐男朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/tszchungj?igshid=1t27gyeu40hmq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ftszchungj%3Figshid%3D1t27gyeu40hmq&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiicls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=c78f28c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/tszchungj?igshid=1t27gyeu40hmq</a><br />\n杜小姐本人<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/tohasim?igshid=1sl0ic94bxcjz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ftohasim%3Figshid%3D1sl0ic94bxcjz&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiicls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=c4fc5d94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/tohasim?igshid=1sl0ic94bxcjz</a><br />\n<br />\n日日水貨客迫爆大馬路 ,啲鄉黑日日圍威喂已成習慣，無數人扮乞衣喺元朗街頭搵食，其實元朗根本就潛在咗好多問題。<br />\n 加上21/7啲白衫人無差別虐打市民，好多元朗人恥與為伍， 咁多人肯入元朗幫我地本人表示熱烈歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n話本身支持返送中，你係IG做下文宣 po story 都冇做。就當你好似達哥咁，沉默是金。相反嘅係，見到ig 日日飲喜茶食烤魚(無圖)<br />\n依架有手足入黎反黑遊行，你又突然po ig話譴責遊行。因爲遊行班手足擾亂民生同生活，而轉態。<br />\n究竟佢係咪真係住喺元朗 究竟元朗安居樂業咗喺邊度<br />\n定係成班鄉黑、黑警係到搞市民 ，個個送曬中 ，先叫安穩？定係佢本身就係鄉黑嘅一份子？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U29cott.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU29cott.jpg&h=743ce7ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VUACzz8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVUACzz8.jpg&h=a8702032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講下我點識呢條女 大約5-6年前係ig見到條女好正<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QXwx7Xx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQXwx7Xx.jpg&h=941051e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmBVmgU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmBVmgU.jpg&h=f2470b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/maStGhF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmaStGhF.jpg&h=cccd15f3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D9bx7XG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD9bx7XG.jpg&h=6d32db0f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EmNJva1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEmNJva1.jpg&h=cde6813a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNpLJv2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjNpLJv2.jpg&h=79ee0f9b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ho1m1hH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fho1m1hH.jpg&h=4d87981a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 點知真人咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N3wKeEc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN3wKeEc.jpg&h=3d3b4fbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NaFrsZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNaFrsZc.jpg&h=d18fbe7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8CA5LT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8CA5LT.jpg&h=cc2c51b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d0zzBSy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd0zzBSy.jpg&h=77c91ab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ngAnLLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FngAnLLU.jpg&h=69fa1e49&s