,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:40:57.000Z","msg":"讀得可道就知咩料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n元朗區爛仔學校：陳震夏，西英，可道，伯裘舊校"},{"pid":"43764bf3d2d7ad4baf5cd6a398ec256b38afd433","tid":1382882,"uid":162906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:54:55.000Z","msg":"嘩, 好撚豬. 怪物黎架.."},{"pid":"604028694bcd108adb3d237592041920290b7728","tid":1382882,"uid":152815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:55:53.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"453978423a0a49dd89096c5454e0b2f26bbf2e83","tid":1382882,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:56:58.000Z","msg":"8月5號大罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n2047到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"a8d8430f460ede4e26cff6f995068b6e17def82f","tid":1382882,"uid":139156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:16:38.000Z","msg":"肉彈戰車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048e6dc74eaaab78e49cf2b41763060a0a15eaae","tid":1382882,"uid":167658,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:19:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">㸃解咁撚重都可以搭飛機</span>"},{"pid":"92fd23d3e771c8be7dfa44294eb2706baacf741b","tid":1382882,"uid":118592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a88a58a8614e1816ae6903123348a133184abb9","tid":1382882,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:16:11.000Z","msg":"好 油膩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c91ad73317916889caa96a7e679a69a5feaa7e","tid":1382882,"uid":213781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"有冇80kg?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e037516e5c3349b4b55b00c88caac111aa0a60","tid":1382882,"uid":165339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:26:30.000Z","msg":"肥撚過部電單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302dbc516e742e6842ce7feb8773af69e150bfca","tid":1382882,"uid":204808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93a2786723bd6b17929680df08611be7c3300a61","tid":1382882,"uid":22819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:44:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">代朋友Post</span></span><br />\n我同樣作為一住咗係元朗26年嘅人見到佢咁打真係好撚嬲 ！！！<br />\n杜夏嬋<br />\nTel 93390693<br />\n嗇色園可道中學<br />\nIg傳送門:<br />\n杜小姐男朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/tszchungj?igshid=1t27gyeu40hmq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ftszchungj%3Figshid%3D1t27gyeu40hmq&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiicls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=c78f28c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/tszchungj?igshid=1t27gyeu40hmq</a><br />\n杜小姐本人<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/tohasim?igshid=1sl0ic94bxcjz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ftohasim%3Figshid%3D1sl0ic94bxcjz&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiicls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=c4fc5d94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/tohasim?igshid=1sl0ic94bxcjz</a><br />\n<br />\n日日水貨客迫爆大馬路 ,啲鄉黑日日圍威喂已成習慣，無數人扮乞衣喺元朗街頭搵食，其實元朗根本就潛在咗好多問題。<br />\n 加上21/7啲白衫人無差別虐打市民，好多元朗人恥與為伍， 咁多人肯入元朗幫我地本人表示熱烈歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n話本身支持返送中，你係IG做下文宣 po story 都冇做。就當你好似達哥咁，沉默是金。相反嘅係，見到ig 日日飲喜茶食烤魚(無圖)<br />\n依架有手足入黎反黑遊行，你又突然po ig話譴責遊行。因爲遊行班手足擾亂民生同生活，而轉態。<br />\n究竟佢係咪真係住喺元朗 究竟元朗安居樂業咗喺邊度<br />\n定係成班鄉黑、黑警係到搞市民 ，個個送曬中 ，先叫安穩？定係佢本身就係鄉黑嘅一份子？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U29cott.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU29cott.jpg&h=743ce7ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VUACzz8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVUACzz8.jpg&h=a8702032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講下我點識呢條女 大約5-6年前係ig見到條女好正<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QXwx7Xx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQXwx7Xx.jpg&h=941051e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmBVmgU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmBVmgU.jpg&h=f2470b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/maStGhF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmaStGhF.jpg&h=cccd15f3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D9bx7XG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD9bx7XG.jpg&h=6d32db0f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EmNJva1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEmNJva1.jpg&h=cde6813a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNpLJv2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjNpLJv2.jpg&h=79ee0f9b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ho1m1hH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fho1m1hH.jpg&h=4d87981a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 點知真人咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N3wKeEc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN3wKeEc.jpg&h=3d3b4fbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NaFrsZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNaFrsZc.jpg&h=d18fbe7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8CA5LT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8CA5LT.jpg&h=cc2c51b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d0zzBSy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd0zzBSy.jpg&h=77c91ab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ngAnLLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FngAnLLU.jpg&h=69fa1e49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e5fKY5U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe5fKY5U.jpg&h=49f1895e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3UguqLV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3UguqLV.jpg&h=f777ce17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XPWVmjS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXP